name: Repealed
text:
REPEALED.  L 2004, c 3, §4.
Note
  L 2004, c 202, §53 purports to amend this section effective July 1, 2006.
Rules of Court
  Appeal, see HRCP 81(f)(2); Hawaii Rules of Appellate Procedure.
Case Notes
  Order to strike State's objection to petition for consolidation under §501-85 is a final order.  54 H. 276, 506 P.2d 1.
